Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.72,0:00:41.98,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}心の声は　閉じたままで
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.98,0:00:44.19,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}あふれそうなCry
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.24,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}Lost in the noise, drowning inside
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.57,0:00:50.11,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}But I won't break, I will never lose myself
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.11,0:00:52.24,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}So rise again, I find myself
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.24,0:00:56.95,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}僕だけの魔法　探していた
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.37,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}数えきれない　絶望も
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.87,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}崩れ落ちた　理想も
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.08,0:01:06.42,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}一振りの勇気だけ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.42,0:01:09.05,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}Believers, going back, back
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.05,0:01:13.39,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}もう　何千何万回の苦難も　恐れない
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.39,0:01:17.10,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)\blur1}ただ　そこに君がいるから
